洗衣日表示艾德·希兰的开幕“感觉不在我们的可能性范围内” https://www.nme.com/news/music/laundry-day-interview-ed-sheeran-new-york-opening-1975-matty-healy-drake-3757575?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=laundry-day-访谈-ed-sheeran-纽约-开幕-1975-马蒂-希利-德雷克Anagricel DuranWed, 22 May 2024 15:22:29 +0000 Music InterviewsMusic NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3757575 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="洗衣日。图片来源：卡米拉·弗兰奇" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>纽约四人组已接受 NME 采访，破解 TikTok 算法，并由 Drake 和 Matty Healy 等人联合签名，并在 Bowery Ballroom 的两晚门票全部售完</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/laundry-day-interview-ed-sheeran-new-york-opening-1975-matty-healy-drake-3757575">《洗衣日》后称艾德·希兰的开场“感觉不在我们的可能性范围内”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="洗衣日。图片来源：卡米拉·弗兰奇" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/laundry-day">Laundry Day</a>与<em>NME</em>谈论了为<a href="/artists/Ed-Sheeran">Ed Sheeran</a>提供开场机会、了解<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/tiktok">TikTok</a>算法、获得<a href="/artists/drake">Drake</a>和<a href="/artists/Jack-Harlow">Jack Harlow</a>等人的赞扬以及他们的返校演出门票售罄的情况。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-radar/whats-your-band-called-mate-get-to-know-laundry-day-2581730">伙计，你的乐队叫什么名字？了解洗衣日</a></strong></li></ul><p>Laundry Day 由歌手 Jude Ciulla-Lipkin 和 Sawyer Nunes 以及贝斯手 Henry Pearl 和吉他手 Henry Weingartner 组成，他们在曼哈顿高中一年级时相识。从那时起，他们发行了五张专辑——最近一张是 2023 年的《Younger Than I Was Before》——并继续为<a href="/artists/Neon-Trees">Neon Trees</a> 、 <a href="/artists/The-1975">The 1975</a>和<a href="/artists/Clairo">Clairo</a>等乐队开场。</p><p> 2024 年上半年，他们在 TikTok 上凭借乐队翻唱热门歌曲的视频取得了病毒般的成功。 1975 年乐队的<a href="/artists/Matty-Healy">Matty Healy</a>在他的 Instagram Stories 上转发了一段他们翻唱的《I’m In Love With You》的视频，最近， <a href="/artists/The-Kid-Laroi">The Kid Laroi</a>转发了他们翻唱的其中一首歌曲的有趣内容。</p><p>德雷克 (Drake) 还与他们合唱，发布了他们的歌曲“疯狂、愚蠢、爱”，并告诉他们他已经观看他们的视频很长时间了。他们的剪辑为他们带来了巨大的机会，比如今年早些时候在<a href="/artists/Teezo-Touchdown">Teezo Touchdown</a>的英国和欧洲巡演期间为他开场。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5WGNrgt9DY/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-